node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Andy Ivanov in Мобиль. May be an image of outdoors and text.

node.text:
Hey everyone! I am starting my next personal project, working title «Summer in Mobil’»
It is very interesting for me to develop some local places, and give them some stories. And for all locals such an idea will seem weird )) In turn, I will try to find something unusual in the usual. 
I plan to find a style, come up with a couple of plots, and then put them into small comics.
For now, I will share developments, sketches and searches.  It's going to be a long journey, let's have fun and see what happens.
.
☑️ If you want to support me and my art, you can purchase my Speedpaint pack, link in bio. Thank you!
.
